    "long_instructions": "## Practice Refining a Prompt\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help you refine a generic prompt.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Choose one of the generic prompts below:\r\n\r\n>Help me plan my school schedule\r\n\r\nOR\r\n\r\n>Teach me about playing piano\r\n\r\nOR\r\n\r\n>How do I become a software engineer?\r\n2. Refine the prompt using all 5 key elements:\r\n   - Task\r\n   - Context\r\n   - Format\r\n   - Reference\r\n   - Tone\r\n3. Type your revised prompt into AI Chat. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's response. \r\n4. **Rinse and Repeat**: Keep refining your prompt and entering it into AI Chat until you have a prompt that consistently generates helpful AI output.\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n",
